    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Pillar Details -> Goal: Organize/Inform -> Viz: Styled Lists in Cards -> Interaction: Clickable navigation links -> Justification: Cards provide clear visual separation for thematic content, and lists are the most direct way to present the program topics. Method: HTML/Tailwind. 2. Pillar Synergy -> Goal: Show Relationships -> Viz: Flow Diagram -> Interaction: Static visual -> Justification: A simple, clean diagram built with HTML/CSS effectively communicates the strategic concept of synergy without requiring complex libraries, adhering to the no-SVG/Mermaid constraint. Method: HTML/Tailwind. -->
